019-04-05T08:07:29.000Z","msg":"就咁睇其實幾多限制，保額又唔太夠。<br />\n<br />\n節錄自Darkmoney:<br />\n重點一：醫療保障額<br />\n<br />\n保障有個別項目上限，易失預算<br />\n<br />\n自願醫保計劃會在每個保障項目增設上限，譬如手術費的帳項是12萬，在VHIS標準計劃中最多只能賠償其中5萬，剩餘7萬便要投保人自付；雖然部份靈活計劃能再保障超支的80%，但這個部份的限額只有8萬-20萬(視不同計劃而定)，未必足夠應付嚴重疾病<br />\n<br />\n自願醫保在「非手術癌症治療」的限額為$80,000，癌症治療的保額明顯不足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.darkmoneyhk.com/single-post/自願醫保-四大重點助你睇清自願醫保的限制\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.darkmoneyhk.com%2Fsingle-post%2F%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%86%AB%E4%BF%9D-%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8D%E9%BB%9E%E5%8A%A9%E4%BD%A0%E7%9D%87%E6%B8%85%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E9%86%AB%E4%BF%9D%E7%9A%84%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6&d=oUHbLHmoFTyfHyZ%2Brcpj5HaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=de598367\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.darkmoneyhk.com/single-post/自願醫保-四大重點助你睇清自願醫保的限制</a>"},{"pid":"3f67abaeba52bba758bde63b3ffdca9a8568577d","tid":1090000,"uid":155674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feec7f9c82f1d579ce2645fcbaee5f4a5d820e03","tid":1090000,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2213fc344ae60dc03fad654d68954b68c8da862","tid":1090000,"uid":155674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94dc1cdbcd9c836410f9074f7b9757da60a2d487","tid":1090000,"uid":102701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"有agent跟填claim表,易好多<br />\n當重病入院,仲會識研究點填表claim?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:12:01.000Z","msg":"搵個好agent都係難過中六合彩<br />\n上次老母個agent冇做之後 變左孤兒單<br />\nclaim錢慘過食屎<br />\n佢兒家都怕左跟agent 學我買網上保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T08:36:52.000Z","msg":"網上買又係自己claim,孤兒單又係自己claim,唔知有咩分別"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:46:16.000Z","msg":"起碼網上買有哂procedure跟住去claim<br />\n你孤兒單都唔知邊個先幫到你<br />\n你推我時我推你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />